data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING A 2% CLOSING COST INCENTIVE FOR BUYER TO USE FOR CASH TO CLOSE, INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN, ETC. PAID FOR BY THE SELLER WITH REASONABLE OFFER. Welcome home to Madora Drive in Spartanburg, South Carolina. This beautiful ranch home is move-in ready and has plenty to offer. The main floor of the home offers a newly updated kitchen, new granite counter-tops, updated flooring throughout, a master suite with completely updated en suite full bath, and two additional bedrooms. A new lighting package and updated and functional bonus room on the main floor adds potential for an additional bedroom, apartment, or family room. The backyard boasts a newly updated back deck and lots of space for entertaining or room for kids or furry friends to roam. Don’t miss the opportunity to own a great house in a quiet neighborhood that is just minutes from everything Spartanburg has to offer. Welcome home to 112 Madora Drive.
